# ============================================================
# PsO PA Pipeline — Environment Configuration
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your key(s).
#
# The pipeline auto-selects the backend in this priority order:
#   GROQ_API_KEY present  → uses Groq (llama-3.3-70b-versatile)
#   GEMINI_API_KEY present → uses Gemini (gemini-3.1-flash-lite)
#   Neither present       → falls back to local Ollama
#
# For the interactive UI (app.py) or bulk run (run_full_pipeline.py)
# you only need ONE of the two keys below.
# ============================================================

# Option A — Groq (recommended for presentation)
# Get your key at: https://console.groq.com
GROQ_API_KEY=your_groq_api_key_here

# Option B — Gemini Flash Lite (free tier: 15 RPM, 500 RPD)
# Get your key at: https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here
